        "description": {
            "name": "description",
            "type": "java.lang.String",
            "value": "When using\r\n_resources.mail.transport.type = sendmail_\r\nin _application.ini_ , _Zend_Mail_Transport_Sendmail::_sendMail()_ detects _$this->parameters_ as en empty string instead of _null_, (line 101). So, php mail() function is used with a fifth parameter (line 126) that contains an empty string. It's a problem as this fifth parameter seems to be forbiden in safe mode.\r\n\r\nA workaround is not to use _resources.mail.transport.type = sendmail_ in _application.ini_ as _sendmail_ is the default transport anyway.\r\n\r\nThanks"
        },
